teo.isgci.gui

Class NulGraphics

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Graphics
      • teo.isgci.gui.NulGraphics

  • public class NulGraphics
extends java.awt.Graphics
    A bitbucket Graphics, that creates no output, but can be used for obtaining the size of painted strings.
